        48 HOURS IN BERLIN - A CREATIVE<br />GUIDE TO INSPIRATION
      </h1>
      <div
        style="text-align: center; max-width: 620px; margin: 16px auto 30px auto; font-size:15px; color:#222;"
      >
        Berlin is Europe’s creative melting pot – full of art, design, street
        culture, and hidden corners that spark inspiration. Whether you’re
        studying, freelancing, or just exploring, here’s how to spend two days
        in the city like a true creative – with budget-friendly cafés, inspiring
        galleries, and unforgettable urban vibes.
      </div>
